rows.label: qst700403_msg0001
rows.name: Hey! Where do you think you're going?!

rows.label: qst700403_msg0002
rows.name:
Retreating to regroup? I didn't
think Gogols were capable of
strategic thinking.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0004
rows.name:
It appears somebody may be
leading them. So, what now?

rows.label: qst700403_msg0005
rows.name:
I say we go after the leader. Take them
out of the picture and the Gogols will
be up a creek without a paddle.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0006
rows.name:
I agree. They'll be hard-pressed to
make a comeback after that.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0007
rows.name:
Exactly! And I mean, we're all
professionals here, right? It's not
like they'll give us any trouble.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0010
rows.name: They are NOT getting away this time.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0011
rows.name:
Haha! I'm starting to wonder if I'll
even have to lift my sword.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0012
rows.name: I think you'll find that's my line!

rows.label: qst700403_msg0013
rows.name:
All right, then let's focus our efforts
on finding the large one.

rows.label: qst700403_msg0014
rows.name:
We should be able to reach higher
ground from the left-hand side.
